import React from 'react';
import { Col, Row } from 'react-bootstrap';
import styles from "./Myposts.module.css"
import Post from './Post/Post'

const Myposts = () =>{
    return(
        <Col xs='12'>
            <Row>
                <Col xs='12'>
                    <textarea></textarea>
                    <button>Add post</button>
                </Col>
            </Row>
            <Post />
            <Row>
                <Col xs='12' className={styles.item}>Post 2</Col>
            </Row>
            <Row>
                <Col xs='12' className={styles.item}>Post 3</Col>
            </Row>
            <Row>
                <Col xs='12'className={styles.item}>Post 4</Col>
            </Row>
        </Col>
    );
}
export default Myposts;
